{"word":"μαγεύω","slug":"μαγεύω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μαγεύω</b></el> <el>(μᾰγεύω,) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:Μάγος'><el>Μάγος</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be a Magus, use magic arts</i>, <b><a href='S:Plutarch'>Plut.</a></b>: <a href='S:cum'>c.</a> <a href='S:accusative'>acc.</a> cogn., <el>μέλη μ.</el> to sing incantations, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:transitive'>trans.</a> <i>to call forth by magic arts</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}